---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="relative border-t border-white/[0.04] bg-urban-dark overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-neon-lime/[0.015] to-transparent pointer-events-none" />

  <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 sm:py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="grid gap-10 sm:gap-12 grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3">

      <div>
        <span class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-display font-black tracking-tight">
          <span class="text-neon-lime glow-text-lime">RF</span><span class="text-urban-white">MUSIC</span>
        </span>
        <p class="mt-3 sm:mt-4 text-xs sm:text-sm text-urban-gray/50 leading-relaxed max-w-xs">
          Sello discografico independiente. Distribucion oficial via The Orchard.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 class="text-xs font-semibold text-urban-white uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4 sm:mb-5">Navegacion</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2 sm:space-y-3">
          <li><a href="/" class="text-sm text-urban-gray/50 hover:text-neon-lime transition-colors">Home</a></li>
          <li><a href="/artistas" class="text-sm text-urban-gray/50 hover:text-neon-lime transition-colors">Artistas</a></li>
          <li><a href="/contacto" class="text-sm text-urban-gray/50 hover:text-neon-lime transition-colors">Contacto</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 class="text-xs font-semibold text-urban-white uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4 sm:mb-5">Legal</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2 sm:space-y-3">
          <li><a href="/aviso-legal" class="text-sm text-urban-gray/50 hover:text-neon-lime transition-colors">Aviso Legal</a></li>
          <li><a href="/politica-privacidad" class="text-sm text-urban-gray/50 hover:text-neon-lime transition-colors">Politica de Privacidad</a></li>
          <li><a href="/politica-cookies" class="text-sm text-urban-gray/50 hover:text-neon-lime transition-colors">Politica de Cookies</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 sm:mt-14 pt-6 sm:pt-8 border-t border-white/[0.04] flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-3 sm:gap-4">
      <p class="text-xs text-urban-gray/35">&copy; {year} Rhyme Flow Music. Todos los derechos reservados.</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-urban-gray/35">Distribuido por The Orchard</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
